::Cygnar::
       He glares angrily at Empath, the hatred in his mind clearly showing in 
his face.  He then turns back to Galvatron.  "Sir, they are well armed, 
inside a base that even they can defend and outnumber us by an amount I doubt 
even I could overcome.  We need troops first.  Preferably troops we don't 
care about, say captured enemies?"  He grins maniacally.

--part1_11d.1572597c.2a8ea5e9_boundary
